fields.title: MSI GeForce RTX 2080S GAMING X TRIO
fields.description: The MSI GeForce RTX 2080 Super Gaming X Trio is a high-end graphics card with the GeForce RTX 2080 SUPER GPU from nVidia. Based on the nVidia Turing architecture, the powerful GeForce RTX 20 graphics card series delivers new levels of gaming realism, speed and performance efficiency, and realistic VR experiences.

fields.title: Asus ROG Crosshair VIII Hero X570
fields.description: The ASUS ROG Crosshair VIII Hero (WI-FI) is a motherboard in ATX format for gamers and overclockers. Two PCIe 4.0 slots in x16 format are available for graphics cards, which are directly connected to the Ryzen 3000 processor via a total of 16 PCIe 4.0 lanes.

fields.title: Corsair Obsidian 750D Airflow Edition
fields.description: The Corsair Obsidian Series 750D Airflow Edition is a full-tower enclosure that offers great conditions for a powerful high-end system. It combines generous expansion flexibility, air and liquid cooling capabilities, and an interior optimized for fast, simple construction and upgrades.

fields.title: Samsung 970 EVO Plus (1000 GB, M.2)
fields.description: Equipped with the latest V-NAND technology, the 970 EVO Plus is even faster than the 970 EVO and also features firmware optimisation. Thanks to NVMe, even greater bandwidth is made possible for even faster access times. It is specifically designed for tech professionals, gamers, and professionals who frequently work on creating and editing videos or simulations.

fields.title: AMD Ryzen 9 5900X
fields.description: The AMD Ryzen 9 5900X is the ultimate desktop processor for gamers, creatives and enthusiasts. AMD's multi-threading technology enables even better multitasking, as each processor core can process two tasks simultaneously. So you can enjoy intelligent multitasking.

fields.title: AMD Ryzen 5 5600X
fields.description: The AMD Ryzen 5 5600X is a processor that is especially aimed at gamers and overclockers. AMD's multi-threading technology enables even better multitasking, because each processor core can process two tasks simultaneously.

fields.title: Gigabyte MB GBT AMD AM4 B550 Aorus Pro V2
fields.description: The Aorus Pro V2 is equipped with the B550 chipset and is suitable for AMD processors with socket AM4. The motherboard supports PCIe 4.0. With its ATX form factor, the Aorus Pro V2 fills the motherboard trays of common cases and offers numerous expansion options.

fields.title: NZXT H510 Elite
fields.description: The NZXT H510 Elite is a successor of the H500i. Like its predecessors, the Midi Tower offers a proven, straightforward design. NZXT installs the Smart Device V2 to control fans and RGB LED accessories and refreshes the front panel with new connectors. In addition, not only the left side panel, but also the front of the H510 Elite is made of tempered glass.

fields.title: Corsair iCUE 465X RGB
fields.description: The CORSAIR iCUE 465X RGB is a smart mid-tower ATX housing with brilliant optics and tempered glass panes. Three integrated CORSAIR LL120 RGB fans and the intelligent RGB lighting control iCUE Lighting Node CORE, in combination with powerful iCUE software, provide instant, fully configurable lighting.

fields.title: Corsair Vengeance LPX
fields.description: The Vengeance LPX memory is specially designed for high performance overclocking. The heat distributor is made of pure aluminum to dissipate heat faster, while the custom-made high performance PCB channels the heat and offers excellent overclocking potential. Each integrated circuit was individually tested for maximum performance potential.

fields.title: G.Skill Trident Z RGB
fields.description: The new G. Skill Trindent Z RGB series offers powerful solutions with integrated LEDS for high-quality configurations. These kits optimize next-generation platforms and are an ideal solution for overclocking. With its colourful and slim design you give your machine the look of your dreams.
